nomic-embed-text (768) & 100.0\% & 93.3\% & 87.5\% & 48.3\% \\
all-minilm (384) & 100.0\% & 42.3\% & 7.5\% & 1.7\% \\
mxbai-embed-large (1024) & 100.0\% & 72.1\% & 2.5\% & 1.0\% \\
ESM-2 (320) & 100.0\% & 44.2\% & 28.7\% & 4.2\% \\
